\mathcal{f}: \mathbb{N} \times \mathbb{N} \times \mathbb{N} \rightarrow\lbrack0,1]
t\geq0
 \mathcal{f}\left( u, d, t\right)  =\left\{ \begin{array} [c]{lll} 0 &  & t=0\\ \frac{u}{u+d+\frac{1}{t}} &  & \text{otherwise} \end{array} \right. 
